<h2>Identity Verification — Action Required</h2>
<p>Hi {{name}},</p>
<p>Unfortunately, we were unable to verify your identity at this time.</p>
{{#if rejectionReason}}
<p><strong>Reason:</strong> {{rejectionReason}}</p>
{{/if}}
<p>You can re-submit your identity documents at any time. Please ensure:</p>
<ul>
  <li>Your documents are clear and not expired</li>
  <li>The document matches the name on your account</li>
  <li>Photos are taken in good lighting without glare</li>
</ul>
<a href="{{appUrl}}/settings/kyc" class="cta">Re-submit Verification</a>
<p style="font-size:13px; color:#6b7280;">If you believe this is an error, please contact <a href="mailto:support@penyzen.com">support@penyzen.com</a>.</p>
